# ⚠️ BEFORE ANY CSS CHANGE: Read S44-INVARIANTS.md!
# Must preserve ALL existing --glass-* tokens (exact values).
# New --touch-* tokens are ADDITIVE — do not modify existing tokens.
# Light/dark theme differences in glass tokens are intentional — do not normalize.

###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Define CSS custom properties for touch target sizes. Single source of truth.
No more ad-hoc h-8, h-9, h-10 etc — all interactive sizing through tokens.

###############################################################################
# TOKENS TO DEFINE (in index.css :root)
###############################################################################

```css
/* ========== Touch Target Tokens ========== */

/* Minimum touch target (Apple HIG / WCAG 2.5.5) */
--touch-min: 44px;          /* 2.75rem — absolute minimum for any interactive element */

/* Standard sizes */
--touch-target-sm: 44px;    /* 2.75rem — icon buttons, toggles, small actions */
--touch-target: 48px;       /* 3rem    — standard buttons, inputs, list items */
--touch-target-lg: 56px;    /* 3.5rem  — primary CTA, prominent actions */

/* Spacing between targets */
--touch-gap: 8px;           /* 0.5rem  — minimum gap between interactive elements */

/* Input heights */
--input-height: 48px;       /* 3rem    — all text inputs */
--input-height-sm: 44px;    /* 2.75rem — compact inputs (search in header) */

/* List items */
--list-item-min-h: 56px;    /* 3.5rem  — tappable list rows */
--list-item-compact: 48px;  /* 3rem    — dense lists (modal pickers) */

/* Navigation */
--nav-item-h: 56px;         /* 3.5rem  — bottom tab bar items */
--header-h: 48px;           /* 3rem    — mobile header height */
```

