###############################################################################
# IMPLEMENTATION
###############################################################################
steps:
  1. Add --touch-* tokens to index.css :root {}
  2. Update button.tsx size variants to use new heights
  3. Update input.tsx default height
  4. Add .touch-area utility class for expanding hit area of visually small elements:
     ```css
     .touch-area {
       position: relative;
     }
     .touch-area::after {
       content: '';
       position: absolute;
       inset: -8px; /* expand by 8px in all directions */
       /* Makes a 28px element have 44px hit area */
     }
     ```
  5. Verify build passes

